{"title":"win下文件快速定位","uid":"b97b67ba25f1a6aa8ccadb4743429614","slug":"win下文件快速定位","date":"2023-12-29T07:50:49.000Z","updated":"2024-04-24T12:17:25.018Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/win下文件快速定位.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Vegetabhl/Images/master/img/9d8a747ee8d94e598a50cc8b03f33fc4_2.png","content":"<h2 id=\"win下文件快速定位\"><a href=\"#win下文件快速定位\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"win下文件快速定位\"></a>win下文件快速定位</h2><p>1 递归查找某一路径下文件夹命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">dir /s aaa*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>首先进入指定目录D:\\Git，递归查询当前目录及其子目录下以首字母是aaa命名的文件夹</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/win%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D.htm/Users\\bhl\\AppData\\Roaming\\Typora\\typora-user-images\\image-20231231220603371.png\" alt=\"image-20231231220603371\"></p>\n<p>2  递归查找某一路径下文件命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">where /r F:\\ aa*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/post/win%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D.htm/Users\\bhl\\AppData\\Roaming\\Typora\\typora-user-images\\image-20231231220630669.png\" alt=\"image-20231231220630669\"></p>\n<p>不需要提前进入指定目录，在命令中输入对应目录，递归查找当前输入目录及其子目录下首字母是aa命名的文件。</p>\n","feature":null,"text":"win下文件快速定位1 递归查找某一路径下文件夹命令： 1dir /s aaa* 首先进入指定目录D:\\Git，递归查询当前目录及其子目录下以首字母是aaa命名...","permalink":"/post/win下文件快速定位","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":177,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#win%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">win下文件快速定位</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Vegetabhl","slug":"blog